    {
      "para_id": "Q000881.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , Piriĝ-me , ruler of Lagaš , child of Ur-Ninĝirsu , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , whose name was proclaimed by Ninĝirsu , the child born by Ninsumun , constructed a weir on the Ursaĝ-ani canal ."
    }
  ],
